@startuml journey-dev-coverage
' ============================================================
' Developer View: End-to-End Journey x Automated Test Coverage
'
' Same journey backbone as journey-end-to-end, recolored by test coverage so
' the diagram doubles as a Playwright/e2e gap map.
'
'   GREEN  = exercised end-to-end by a Playwright spec (frontend/e2e/*.spec.ts)
'   AMBER  = built, but only unit/component tested (frontend/src/**/*.test.tsx)
'            -> the remaining e2e backlog
'   RED    = no automated test (mostly planned / not-yet-built steps)
'   GREY   = backend work, covered by pytest, out of frontend-e2e scope
'
' Coverage sources (frontend/e2e/*.spec.ts, current set):
'   reader, reader-conflict, reader-reload-resume, library, intake,
'   guardian-auth, guardian-console, guardian-review, guardian-profiles,
'   guardian-books, assignments, profiles, story-requests,
'   story-requests-kid, story-requests-authored, series-continue, landing,
'   admin-user-management (#267), authoring-queue (#268), device-authorization,
'   moderation, provider-allowlist, a11y, visual, and e2e/naive-user/*
'   frontend/e2e-real/{approval-flow,authored-request,kid-reads,
'     naive-kid-misuse-real,series-continue-real,authoring-plan-real,
'     moderation-real,ratings-real}.spec.ts  (real-backend smoke, zero mocks)
'   frontend/e2e-prod/ and frontend/e2e-staging/ (deployed-env smoke, own configs)
'   frontend/src/**/*.test.ts(x)  (Vitest component + unit)
' ============================================================

title Developer View: Journey x Test Coverage\n(green = e2e, amber = unit-only [e2e backlog], red = none, grey = backend/pytest)

skinparam defaultFontName "Roboto"
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundCorner 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowColor #5a3e28
skinparam ArrowFontColor #5a3e28
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FFFDF8
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #6b6b56
skinparam ActivityDiamondBackgroundColor #f8f3e8
skinparam ActivityDiamondBorderColor #8c6f56
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #F1E9D8
skinparam NoteBorderColor #c9b48f
skinparam swimlaneWidth same

|#F0D9B8|Child|
|#CDDCEC|Guardian|
|#C5D9CC|Admin|
|#E4E4E4|System|

|Guardian|
